    <item>
      <title>Ecopetrol Eyes Carlyle的哥伦比亚资产以增强储量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/ecopetrol-eyes-buying-carlyle-s-colombia-asset-to-boost-reserves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚的最高高管在接受采访时说，哥伦比亚国有的Ecopetrol SA正在考虑购买凯雷集团在全国范围内购买的石油钻机，因为它希望提高储备和产出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/ecopetrol-eyes-buying-carlyle-s-colombia-asset-to-boost-reserves</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 23:54:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
